          "reviewBody": "The worst school of faridabad. Teachers here don't know atticates , they literally itch private parts of their body in front of students. They have 5 diffrent dresses for five different days.  Even after being a popular school some Teachers don't even know English. And the sports department they think that they are the one who made the school and talk very rudely to students. They don't even teach the basic concepts and put higher level difficult questions. They give a lotta written work and say to finish it within the day. They just send ppts of large numbers of slides. Teachers are partiall towards some students too. And tell us the importance of not going to coachings and tutions. They think that school is enough to study . Jealous of us going to coachings. Some teachers don't even know the proper name of students and in ptm they demotivate the child so much. Even after being a cbse affiliated school they don't prefer ncert especially in maths.",
